Text: RE Im Leaving Enronwishes I enjoyed working with you Hope you stay in touch Marc Original Message From mailto Sent Friday March AM To KADDENCOM kaddencom AddressListTooLongSuppressed Subject Im Leaving Enron I am going to be the Senior Regulatory Counsel at ISO New England starting on April My last day in the Portland area will be March I enjoyed working with you and wish you the best of everything My new address will be Mary Hain Senior Regulatory Counsel ISO New England Inc One Sullivan Road Holyoke MA SONEcom
